ampaigns camp ON camp.id = c.campaign_id\n```\n- `challenges` table has a `campaign_id` foreign key\n- `campaigns` table has an `id` and `campaign_type` field (e.g., \"daily\", \"weekly\", \"onboarding\")\n- Each campaign can have multiple challenges filtered by `is_active = true`\n\n### Key Config Pattern\n- Admin routes validate against a hardcoded set: `VALID_CONFIG_KEYS` (admin.ts, lines 14-26)\n- Config values stored in `reward_config` table with `key`, `value`, `updated_at` columns\n- Routes query this table for configuration (challenges.ts uses `readRewardConfig()`)"}],"totalDurationMs":10475,"totalTokens":43674,"totalToolUseCount":3,"usage":{"input_tokens":4302,"cache_creation_input_tokens":12024,"cache_read_input_tokens":26838,"output_tokens":510,"server_tool_use":{"web_search_requests":0,"web_fetch_requests":0},"service_tier":"standard","cache_creation":{"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":12024},"inference_geo":"","iterations":[],"speed":"standard"}}}
